Phase 9 Tasks 1-2: Clipboard Integration

Files changed:
  - src/input/clipboard.rs: new clipboard module
  - src/input/mod.rs: added pub mod clipboard
  - Cargo.toml: added arboard = "3" dependency

Implementation:
  - is_copy_keybinding(): Cmd+C (macOS/Super) or Ctrl+Shift+C (Linux)
  - is_paste_keybinding(): Cmd+V (macOS/Super) or Ctrl+Shift+V (Linux)
  - Ctrl+C alone NOT detected as copy (it's terminal interrupt)
  - wrap_bracketed_paste(): wraps text in \x1b[200~ ... \x1b[201~
  - paste_bytes(): raw text or bracketed-wrapped based on mode flag

Tests (12 new, 283 total):
  - Copy keybinding: Cmd+C, Ctrl+Shift+C, Ctrl+C not copy, wrong key (4)
  - Paste keybinding: Cmd+V, Ctrl+Shift+V, Ctrl+V not paste (3)
  - Bracketed paste: wraps text, empty string (2)
  - Paste bytes: without/with bracketed mode, UTF-8 content (3)

Quality gates: 283 tests pass, clippy clean, fmt clean
